**** PARCEL BUNDLER ****
- npm init -y
- npm install --save-dev -g parcel // global installation
- parcel build home.html // build your app for production or testing
- in netlify (or if errors with minifying occurs), use "--no-minify" option
// in the package.json file edit this part:
"scripts": {
    "start": "parcel home.html" //i think that this command runs when ever npm is started, and it builds the app
  }